config BR2_PACKAGE_UNCLUTTER
	bool "unclutter"
    depends on BR2_PACKAGE_XLIB_LIBX11
	help
      Unclutter runs in the background of an X11 session and after a specified period of inactivity hides the cursor from display. 
      When the cursor is moved its display is restored. 
      Users may specify specific windows to be ignored by unclutter.

	  https://sourceforge.net/projects/unclutter/
